==Other==
[[File:Dragon plateskirt (g) equipped.png|thumb|100px|A player with gilded dragon armour equipped.]]
Ornamental dragon armour and weapons have the same bonuses as their standard counterparts. Unlike most other [[ornamental armour|ornamental items]], ornamental dragon armour is obtained by using [[ornament kit]]s on the specific items. These ornament kits can be obtained from the member's only [[Treasure Trails]] minigame.

